id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>σεν̣\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.1)\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">ἔτη\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Στατειλία Θεαγενὶς\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Στατειλία\">ΣΤΑΤΕΙΛΙΑ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Θεαγενὶς\">ΘΕ\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>ΑΓΕΝΙΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔζησεν\">ΕΖ\u003Cspan class=\"small\" title=\"small character: η\">Η\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΣΕ.\u003C/span> &nbsp;&nbsp; \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">ΕΤΗ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001326_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001326_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001326.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001326-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on photographs\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0001-7077-0703\">Alex Antoniou\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Stateilia Theagenis lived for [?] years.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Statilia Theagenis visse [?] anni.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The epitaph presents the name of the deceased and the indication of her age (the years are assumed to be in a missing fourth line). The gentilicium \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Στατείλια\u003C/span> is also found in the Latin funerary inscription of the 2nd-3rd century CE, CIL 10.7094 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000376\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000376\u003C/a>. The name \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Θεαγενίς\u003C/span> is not well attested (for the masculine form \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Θεαγένης\u003C/span> attested in South Italy, see LGPN 3A 199). For \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Θεαγενίς\u003C/span> in two urban inscriptions, see Solin 1982: 84.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ferrara 1829 391 no.6 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Kaibel 1890 \u003Ca href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">505\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 133 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>Letters with serifs: Ε and Σ lunate, Η at l. 2 in smaller size.\u003C/p> Lines 1-3  20-30  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[232,235,238,241,244,246,249,252,255],{"id":233,"html":234},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Στατειλία Θεαγενὶς\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Στατειλία\">Στατειλία\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Θεαγενὶς\">Θε-\u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>αγενὶς\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔζησεν\">ἔζ\u003Cspan class=\"small\" title=\"small character: η\">η\u003C/span>-\u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>σεν̣\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.1)\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">ἔτη\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Στατειλία Θεαγενὶς\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Στατειλία\">ΣΤΑΤΕΙΛΙΑ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Θεαγενὶς\">ΘΕ\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>ΑΓΕΝΙΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔζησεν\">ΕΖ\u003Cspan class=\"small\" title=\"small character: η\">Η\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΣΕ.\u003C/span> &nbsp;&nbsp; \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">ΕΤΗ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":236,"html":237},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001326_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001326_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001326.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001326-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>",{"id":239,"html":240},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on photographs\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":242,"html":243},"translation","\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0001-7077-0703\">Alex Antoniou\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Stateilia Theagenis lived for [?] years.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":242,"html":245},"\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Statilia Theagenis visse [?] anni.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":247,"html":248},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The epitaph presents the name of the deceased and the indication of her age (the years are assumed to be in a missing fourth line). The gentilicium \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Στατείλια\u003C/span> is also found in the Latin funerary inscription of the 2nd-3rd century CE, CIL 10.7094 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000376\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000376\u003C/a>. The name \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Θεαγενίς\u003C/span> is not well attested (for the masculine form \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Θεαγένης\u003C/span> attested in South Italy, see LGPN 3A 199). For \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Θεαγενίς\u003C/span> in two urban inscriptions, see Solin 1982: 84.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":250,"html":251},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ferrara 1829 391 no.6 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Kaibel 1890 \u003Ca href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">505\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 133 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":253,"html":254},"handnote","\u003Cp>Letters with serifs: Ε and Σ lunate, Η at l. 2 in smaller size.\u003C/p> Lines 1-3  20-30  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  ",{"id":256,"html":257},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[259,261,264,265],{"html":260},"Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo",{"id":262,"lang":128,"html":263},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Στατειλία Θεαγενὶς\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Στατειλία\">Στατειλία\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Θεαγενὶς\">Θε-\u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>αγενὶς\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔζησεν\">ἔζ\u003Cspan class=\"small\" title=\"small character: η\">η\u003C/span>-\u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>σεν̣\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.1)\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">ἔτη\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"html":260},{"id":266,"lang":128,"html":267},"edition-diplomatic","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Στατειλία Θεαγενὶς\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Στατειλία\">ΣΤΑΤΕΙΛΙΑ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Θεαγενὶς\">ΘΕ\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>ΑΓΕΝΙΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔζησεν\">ΕΖ\u003Cspan class=\"small\" title=\"small character: η\">Η\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΣΕ.\u003C/span> &nbsp;&nbsp; \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">ΕΤΗ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",[269,271],{"image":104,"thumb":270,"title":107},"ISic001326_tiled-thumb.tif",{"image":272,"thumb":273,"title":107},"ISic001326.jpg","ISic001326-thumb.jpg",[275],{"html":60},"\u003C?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>\n\u003C?xml-model href=\"https://epidoc.stoa.org/schema/latest/tei-epidoc.rng\" type=\"application/xml\" schematypens=\"http://relaxng.org/ns/structure/1.0\"?>\n\u003C?xml-model href=\"../schematron/ircyr-checking.sch\" schematypens=\"http://purl.oclc.org/dsdl/schematron\"?>\n\u003CTEI xmlns=\"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n    \u003CteiHeader>\n        \u003CfileDesc>\n            \u003CtitleStmt>\n                \u003Ctitle>Epitaph for Statilia Theagenis\u003C/title>\n                \u003Ceditor ref=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/editor>\n                \u003Cprincipal ref=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/principal>\n                \u003Cfunder>John Fell OUP Research Fund\u003C/funder>\n\t   \u003Cfunder>\u003Cref target=\"https://cordis.europa.eu/project/id/885040\">ERC Advanced Grant no.885040\u003C/ref>\u003C/funder>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"JP\" ref=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>original data collection and editing\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"martaf\" ref=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/na